import React from "react";

const TodoSearch = () => {

    return (
        <Row>
            <Col>
                <Form>
                    <FormControl
                    name="user_id"
                    value="1"
                    type="hidden" 
                    placeholder="New Item" 
                    />
                    <FormControl
                        name="title"
                        value={newItem} 
                        type="text" 
                        placeholder="New Item" 
                    />
                </Form>
            </Col>
            <Col>
                <Button variant="link" onClick={onDelete}>
                    <i className="fa fa-remove text-danger" />
                </Button>
            </Col>
        </Row>
    );

}

export default TodoSearch
